This module implements the MediaTek Thermal HAL.

WHAT IT DOES?
=============
Mediatek Thermal HAL return cpu/gpu/battery/Tskin and cpu usage to framework.


thermal.[platform].so contains the Mediatek thermal HAL.

HOW IT WAS BUILT?
==================
It needs the following library from AOSP:

libandroid, libcutils, liblog and libutils

HOW TO USE IT?
==============
Mediatek thermal HAL should not be used directly by an application.  Most of
thermal hints will be triggered by Android framework service.

The majority of source code for this library were written by MediaTek.  Various
open source libraries are also used and contained in this folder.
